Package: MTP
Title: Implementation of the Multiple Translation Path translation tool
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Andrea",
           family = "Prunotto",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "prunotto@imbi.uni-freiburg.de",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1235-1740"))
Description: The package collects translations from on line tools and produce a list of translation candidates, with score. 
    It needs "docker" and "RSelenium" to be installed (with firefox).
